OL,4,G1700F5 News with Dan Walker
OL,5,     GJoin Dan Walker and the team for
OL,6,     Gthe news that matters to you.
OL,7,G1800FSusan Calman's Grand Day Out
OL,8,     GIn Dorset, Susan explores the
OL,9,     GJurassic Coast and digs in the
OL,10,     Gfootsteps of renowned fossil
OL,11,     Ghunter Mary Anning before moving
OL,12,     Ginto Devon and fulfilling her
OL,13,     Gdream of driving a vintage tram.
OL,14,G1900FPolice Interceptors
OL,15,     GThere's a blistering pursuit on
OL,16,     Gthe M1 as Interceptors chase a
OL,17,     Gvehicle veering across lanes,
OL,18,     Gpushing the speed to 115mph. And
OL,19,     Gwe follow the dog unit as three
OL,20,     Gcanine cops are trained.
